      "rationale": "Boundary conditions (fixed inferior vertebral body, displacement-controlled superior body), contact definitions (frictional, mu=0.3), and material assignments (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, UHMWPE blocks) independently verified by second analyst against ASTM F1717 test setup documentation. No discrepancies identified. Achieved level meets required level."
