      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E/uval) computed for all three QoIs with pre-specified acceptance threshold. Required Gradation 3: validation metric computed with experimental uncertainty quantified and pre-specified acceptance criteria applied.",
      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval computed per FDA guidance for all three QoIs: stiffness (1.41), yield force (1.78), force at 40 mm (1.62). All values below pre-specified threshold of 1.96. Experimental uncertainty estimated from inter-laboratory repeatability data. Pre-specification of acceptance criteria documented prior to data unblinding. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
